h well-studied benefit\nallocations, namely, the Shapley value and the nucleolus. We show that our\nmethod performs better in stability, tractability, and fairness, which would\npotentially be dictated by a criterion chosen by the regulator.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2019 16:48:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-23"}
