entially inform both the\ndesign of turbines and the arrangement of turbines into highly efficient\narrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 20 Dec 2019 21:22:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 23:06:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-01"}
