 i0<7.5deg. However, the\ndepletion of the planetary migration seems to prevent a large fraction of such\norbits, especially for the slow migration model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Dec 2019 15:01:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-04"}
