imated CLuMPA/F and unbound fraction of MPA (FUMPA) in Chinese\nkidney transplant recipients were comparable to those published previously in\nCaucasians. We recommend monitoring uMPA instead of tMPA to optimise\nmycophenolate mofetil (MMF) dosing for patients with lower ALB levels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 21 Dec 2019 03:11:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-24"}
